# combine_init_files.py
combine initial q, p at different temperature for training.

1. settiing MC_parameters (particle, temp, dq ...) and then run prepare_dir.sh
( make run folders and parameters template )
2. run ./cp2parameters.py after resetting parameters.
3. run MC_sampler.py and then generate samples depend on temp each run folder.
4. run combine_init_files.py
5. write pt file for combined samples in n4 folder for train/valid.

e.g)
init_config/n4/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_allT_train_sampled.pt
init_config/n4/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_allT_valid_sampled.pt


# combine_niter_files.py ( for training - write and read in training_data folder )

1. setting MD_parameters (long tau, short tau ...) and then run prepare_dir.sh
2. run ./cp2parameters.py after resetting parameters.
3. run MD_sampler.py and then write file that integrate from combined samples as initial q, p.

e.g)
training_data/run10/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_train_sampled_id0.pt   - from iteration id0
training_data/run11/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_valid_sampled_id0.pt   - from iteration id0

4. concatenate initial q, p and write files (iteration id0), and then create file in n4 folder

e.g) copy initial q, p file in same folder
training_data/run10/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_train_sampled.pt       - initial q, p
training_data/run11/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_valid_sampled.pt

get below files.
training_data/n4/nparticle4_rho0.1_allT_train_sampled.pt
training_data/n4/nparticle4_rho0.1_allT_valid_sampled.pt

# combine_niter_files.py ( for test - write and read in test_data folder)
do more iterations given maximum times. then generate more write files.

training_data/run10/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_test_sampled_id0.pt
training_data/run10/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_test_sampled_id1.pt
training_data/run10/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_test_sampled_id2.pt
training_data/run10/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_test_sampled_id3.pt

e.g) copy initial q, p file in same folder
training_data/run10/nparticle4_new_nsim_rho0.1_T0.04_pos_test_sampled.pt       - initial q, p

get below files.
training_data/n4/run10/nparticle4_rho0.1_T0.04_test_sampled.pt